     FIL0633AUO   E                    PRINTER      KINFDS SPOOLU
      /EJECT
      *----------------------------------------------------------------
      /COPY ZSRSRC,ZDATE2Z1
      /COPY ZSRSRC,ZSEDITZ1
      *
      ***  Array for compilation - copyright insertion
      *
     E                    CPY@    1   1 80
      *
      /EJECT
      *----------------------------------------------------------------
     ISDBANK    E DSSDBANKPD
      ***  Standing Data - Bank Details
      *
      ***  Working Data Structure
      *
     IPSDS       SDS
      ***  Program status data structure for WS/user ID'S
     I                                     *PROGRAM PGM
     I                                      244 253 JOB
     I                                      254 263 USER
      *
     ILDA       E DSLDA                         256
      ***  Local data area
      *
     ISPOOLU      DS
      *
      **  File Information Data Structure - AU report
     I                                       83  92 SFILEU
     I                                    B 123 1240SFNUMU
     ISPOOL1      DS
      *
      **  File Information Data Structure - P1 report
     I                                       83  92 SFIL1
     I                                    B 123 1240SFNUM1
